SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1471 on Page 6, Lines 9 and 10, by deleting all new language in
paragraph 2 and inserting a new paragraph 2 to read as follows:
“ 2. "Plastic" means any synthetic, malleable polymer primarily derived from non-renewable
petrochemical feedstocks that is durable and designed for, or frequently used as, single-use,
conventionally non-biodegradable materials”
